Eastern International University - High quality university in Binh Duong Eastern International University (EIU) is a private university established by Becamex IDC Corporation, one of the leading industrial park developers in Vietnam. The school is located in the center of Binh Duong New City, an urban area being invested by Becamex IDC with an estimated need for high-quality human resources of 150,000 people by 2020. EIU is considered one of the high-quality universities in Vietnam, with advanced training programs, a team of highly qualified and experienced lecturers, and modern facilities. The school has many student clubs and groups that are actively active in fields such as academics, sports, culture, art,... Conclude With the advantages of training programs, lecturers, facilities and student life, EIU is an ideal choice for candidates who wish to study at a high-quality university in Binh Duong. Eastern International University was established by Becamex IDC Corporation, one of the leading industrial park developers in Vietnam. The school is located in the center of Binh Duong New City - an urban area being invested in by Becamex IDC with an estimated need for high-quality human resources of 150,000 people by 2020. In 2009: Construction began on the school after the Prime Minister and the People's Committee of Binh Duong province accepted the policy of establishing the school and approved the detailed planning. 2010: Eastern International University was officially established according to Decision 1789/QD-TTg of the Prime Minister to contribute to implementing the policy of training according to social needs, associating training with social needs. economic development. Especially industrial development, high technology with modern management model. October 3, 2011: Eastern International University held the opening ceremony of the first course. Vision to 2030: Eastern International University aims to become a multi-disciplinary university - multi-field accredited and internationally ranked; and is a cultural center and a leading applied research and technology transfer center in Vietnam. Mission: Eastern International University is a university of businesses (Becamex IDC), operating according to the model of many universities within one university; a place that attracts and concentrates graduate lecturers from many European and American countries; Training students in the direction of research - application, good at both expertise and foreign languages, following the main ideology of close - mutual relations and community service; Training according to practical development needs, contributing to promoting the country's sustainable development. Educational philosophy: Humanity ‚Äì Community ‚Äì Creativity ‚Äì Sustainability. Core values: Proudly serving the community. Training majors: Business Administration, Nursing, Electrical Engineering, Control and Automation Engineering, Mechatronics Engineering, Software Engineering, Computer Networks and Data Communications.
